Job Description
Share
A top branded international 5 star hotel in Dubai is looking for a Chef de Cuisine for their French Restaurant.
It is a contemporary 100 seat (indoor outdoor) open kitchen concept restaurant with two sections, a casual bistro/bar section and a more gourmet section with floor to ceiling Wine and cheese cellars.
We are looking for a young talent, French, male or female, good looking, with excellent presentation and professional skills (1* Michelin level), willing to create a name for himself in Dubai. He/she will conduct cooking demos and classes in the Restaurant.
Desired Candidate Profile
The classes could be filmed and each participant would receive an engraved personalized DVD at the end of the session.
